text_blocks.snippet: SZA is 36 years old (born November 8, 1989). While she was raised in Maplewood, New Jersey, she reportedly resides in Los Angeles, California, a common base for her frequent collaborations and industry presence.
SZA is a multi-talented artist recognized for her unique approach to contemporary R&B and soul.

table: Rolling Stone's 200 Greatest Singers of All Time
Intermediate to Advanced. She has a background in gymnastics and cheerleading and has evolved into a performer who integrates dance and choreography into her live shows and music videos.
Emerging. She made her film debut co-starring in the 2025 comedy One of Them Days.
Non-Instrumentalist. SZA has stated she does not play traditional instruments like guitar or piano, focusing instead on melody and lyric creation directly into a microphone.
